From 00cf1d90ac748838e53196a6031234139c4df1a2 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mahesh Balla <mahesh.balla@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 6 Apr 2026 11:25:36 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Restructure blog from generic Astro template to Oracle EPM
 Cloud product-based navigation

Replace the default blog structure with product-specific routes for EPM Cloud Updates,
Narrative Reporting, and Planning Cloud. Each product has subcategory pages for Tutorials,
Tips, Use Cases, and Latest Release. Adds dropdown navigation, breadcrumbs, and sample articles.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
